[SDG-WAYSHELL]: Brightness OSD appears when moving cursor to the left edge of any monitor
[SDG-WAYSHELL]: Screenshot toolbar appears at the top-center of any monitor
[SDG-WAYSHELL]: Monocle bars show window switchers per monitor when in monocle/deck layouts
[SDG-WAYSHELL]: Elevated (root/sudo) processes are listed in the bottom-left zone
[SDG-WAYSHELL]: Focused process CPU, RAM, and GPU usage in the bottom-right zone
[SDG-WAYSHELL]: Layout-switching bars change automatically — no manual toggle needed
[SDG-WAYSHELL]: Config hot-reload: `pkill wayshell && wayshell &` picks up changes to wayshell.conf and wayshell.modules
